high_descs: Turn to the left, Head to the stove
Pick up the yellow knife from the counter
Turn to the right, Head to the sink
Open the cabinet door under the sink
Put knife in cabinet
Take plate and knife from the cabinet
Put the plate and knife in the sink
anns.task_desc: Take the yellow knife and plate from under the sink, put them in the sink

high_descs: Move to stand at the counter directly to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Carry the knife to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Open the cupboard on the left beneath the sink and place the knife on the pan inside.
Pick up the pan with the knife on it from the cupboard.
Carry the pan and knife closer to the kitchen sink.
Place the pan and knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife on a pan in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left head to the counter beside the stove
Pick up the knife beside the the toaster on the counter
Turn to your right move forward then turn to the sink on your left
Open the drawer under the small sink and put the knife on the basin
Pick up the plate with knife then close the drawer
Turn around to your right then turn back to your left then go forward to the sink
Place the plate with knife on the smaller sink
anns.task_desc: Place the plate with knife in the sink.
